    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Strip of lace, cloth, leather, or another material that is gathered on one edge or cut on the bias, so that when attached to the hem, button placard, neckline, or wrist of a garment it produces an ornamental frill or flounce.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
